{"tid":1982220,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"三大支資航企準備接管維珍航空","createTime":"2020-04-21T05:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T15:58:54.000Z","uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c0ee429aec1ceb3a90594a4f46f87491b43870a9","tid":1982220,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:39:57.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】路透社昨日報道，在<del>新冠</del>武漢肺炎疫情下陷入財困的維珍澳洲航空，正準備進入自願接管（voluntary administration）程序。有澳媒更引述消息人士表示，預計維珍澳洲或最快在當地時間今日內正式宣布自願接管。在澳洲制度下，自願接管可以讓公司選擇透過資產出售、註銷債務或公司清盤等方法償還債務。維珍澳洲拒絕評論有關消息。<br />\n<br />\n另外，據外媒披露，海航持有維珍澳洲20%股份，新加坡航空及阿提哈德航空則分別持有20%及21%股權，維珍集團僅持10%，然而這些公司的財務狀况亦因為疫情大流行而急劇惡化。截至去年12月底止，維珍澳洲所公布的中期業績錄得虧損8860萬澳元（約4.39億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n傳三大中資航企洽購<br />\n評級機構穆迪上周五下調維珍澳洲航空的評級，理由是不論維珍澳洲的後續如何發展，都會導致債券持有人的債務減值。截至去年12月底，維珍澳洲航空債務總額為50億澳元（約246億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n日前市場曾有消息傳出，內地三大中資航空公司，中國南方航空（1055）、東方航空（0670）及國航（0753）正討論是否收購維珍澳洲航空，以防止其「災難性」倒閉。不過，三家航空公司均未提出正式報價。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20200421/s00004/1587408750512/%E6%BE%B3%E5%AA%92-%E7%B6%AD%E7%8F%8D%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E6%93%AC%E8%87%AA%E9%A1%98%E6%8E%A5%E7%AE%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20200421%2Fs00004%2F1587408750512%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E7%258F%258D%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E6%2593%25AC%25E8%2587%25AA%25E9%25A1%2598%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25AE%25A1&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiUoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=b8c556f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%2Farticle%2F20200421%2Fs00004%2F1587408750512%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E7%258F%258D%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E6%2593%25AC%25E8%2587%25AA%25E9%25A1%2598%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25AE%25A1&h=47859980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F/article/20200421/s00004/1587408750512/%E6%BE%B3%E5%AA%92-%E7%B6%AD%E7%8F%8D%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E6%93%AC%E8%87%AA%E9%A1%98%E6%8E%A5%E7%AE%A1</a>"},{"pid":"be68119c328f2fbff0c4765803b3d8c52a827ef6","tid":1982220,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:44:10.000Z","msg":"其實有幾多間財困既公司同海航無關係"},{"pid":"398736497b6ae633222f8c7acedecdacd5980ef5","tid":1982220,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"個3間中資自己好多錢咩？"},{"pid":"44a6a24cc4040c829ecf126a8f1accadbac00259","tid":1982220,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T06:47:02.000Z","msg":"中共買哂啲大財團<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1933c4f89b0c8e6c467b8e39dc386ec580a157aa","tid":1982220,"uid":155177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T06:49:51.000Z","msg":"標題誤導<br />\n維珍澳洲航空同維珍航空 2間公司"},{"pid":"319be611409121db57521e543201e5ade94ef8f2","tid":1982220,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"澳洲總理唔係拒絕咩"},{"pid":"34df80fccb037eb4e8dc5e8c8d86d823829ee5fa","tid":1982220,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:23:45.000Z","msg":"所有中資已經融入緊世界"},{"pid":"d993e7fabae36a7e75dde6ecad1f86018ee45d37","tid":1982220,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"弗吉?"}]}